Design Inspiration
------------------
The visual design of Lumio (pastel card colours, typography pairing, and
layout patterns) is inspired by the Array theme for Ghost CMS by Bright Themes
(https://brightthemes.com/themes/array). Array is a commercial Ghost theme;
no code from Array was used or adapted. The WordPress PHP/CSS implementation
of Lumio is entirely original work by Zahid Abbasi, written from scratch
for WordPress, and is licensed under GPL v2 or later.

